{"tid":506243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[趕豬入月台] 又壞！ 港鐵列車無法關門 籲客落車即走","createTime":"2017-12-22T04:06:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-22T20:22:36.000Z","uid":45788,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"703e880156736d50b6c880fb7acdf510d8d49ccf","tid":506243,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T04:06:43.000Z","msg":"再有港鐵列車懷疑失靈。有市民晚上在Facebook「North District 北區」群組上載片段，顯示九龍塘站一列北行往上水方向列車，車門打開，車廂空無一人，但列車正駛離月台。<br />\n<br />\n上載片段的市民指，涉事列車「閂極都閂唔到門」持續幾分鐘，「迫住趕晒全部人落車話故障暫停載客，迫爆晒月台」，形容列車「落荒而逃」，惟仍未能關上車門。網民留言戲稱「咁咪通風啲囉，又唔係唔行得」，亦有人評理指做法合理，「其實只可以咁做啦，唔趕你落車停係（喺）到又會阻住後面」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171222/57612129\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171222%2F57612129&d=3k9qFdqOAHnmvG%2BdGGqsO5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=47e1a93c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171222%2F57612129&h=87c894b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171222/57612129</a>"},{"pid":"474ec9eefcf137f4e5a816d5b44ec14438b0b8b9","tid":506243,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T04:07:38.000Z","msg":"港鐵：sorry,又阻住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bce0d01f40eb90619a5496be18f36dafa035dd5c","tid":506243,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T04:10:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1144e850891c1afc841af3fc9ad26d5fa409814","tid":506243,"uid":13914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T04:11:23.000Z","msg":"開住門開車, 都算係難得奇境"},{"pid":"b6acbfac63326134bcaa03add225f3899ba59a13","tid":506243,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T04:18:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"